<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | LifeVerdict</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for LifeVerdict. Learn how we handle your data.">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .page-content { max-width: 800px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 0 24px; }
        h1 { margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 2.5rem; }
        h2 { margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1.5rem; color: #1e293b; }
        p { line-height: 1.7; color: #475569; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    @template.layout._header()

    <main class="page-content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last Updated: January 1, 2026</p>

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>LifeVerdict ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website.</p>

        <h2>2. Data Collection</h2>
        <p>We do not collect personal identifiable information (PII) unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., newsletter signup). We may use cookies for analytics to improve user experience.</p>

        <h2>3. Use of Information</h2>
        <p>Any information collected is used solely for improving our content, analyzing traffic, and providing the services you request.</p>

        <h2>4. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our site contains links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites.</p>
        
        <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, please contact us at support@lifeverdict.com.</p>
    </main>

    @template.layout._footer()
</body>
</html>
